cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.DL 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and semantic change. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it uses Bayesian models for semantic change. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.DL (Deep Learning) as it deals with information retrieval and uses a dynamic semantic change model.
